CatDescriptText: Cutline of related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 20, 1953, page 22 and 23, reads: "Plenty of Booths, Prizes and Crowds at Courier's Pittsburgh Home Service Fair"
TitMainTitle: Three women, including woman wearing light colored calico dress with gathered sleeves with string tie, gathered with crowd in Ammon Center for the 1953 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
